## COMBINED IMPLEMENTATION STRATEGY

### Phase 1: Foundation (Months 1-6)
**Cybersecurity**: Security compliance, zero-trust, predictive operations
**Genomics**: Sequence processing, regulatory compliance, decision support adaptation

### Phase 2: Expansion (Months 7-12)
**Cybersecurity**: Threat intelligence, incident response, compliance navigator
**Genomics**: Pathogen evolution tracking, population genomics, advanced analytics

### Phase 3: Advanced Integration (Months 13-18)
**Cybersecurity**: Vulnerability management, resilience simulation, privacy analytics
**Genomics**: Epidemiology integration, personalization, predictive operations

### Phase 4: Optimization & Scale (Months 19-24)
**Combined**: Full integration, optimization, global deployment, continuous improvement

