## ENERGY DISTRIBUTION IMPLEMENTATION STRATEGY

### Phase 1: Foundation (Months 1-3)
**Core Operations**: Predictive maintenance (Pattern 7), Decision support (Pattern 3)
**Energy Specific**: Market trading (Pattern 21), GIS intelligence (Pattern 22)

### Phase 2: Expansion (Months 4-6)
**Optimization**: Autonomous optimization (Pattern 14), Orchestration (Pattern 6)
**Energy Specific**: Regulatory compliance (Pattern 23), Multi-modal data fusion (Pattern 24)

### Phase 3: Advanced Capabilities (Months 7-12)
**Intelligence**: Visual intelligence (Pattern 4), Knowledge mining (Pattern 13)
**Energy Specific**: Smart grid resilience (Pattern 25), Customer analytics (Pattern 26)

### Phase 4: Integration & Scale (Months 13-18)
**Full Integration**: All patterns integrated and optimized for energy distribution operations
**Continuous Improvement**: AI-driven optimization and enhancement of all systems

